Task: Create settings configuration manager

Summary:
- Created include/settings_manager.h and src/settings_manager.cpp to manage configuration state (units, brightness, auto brightness, and timezone offset) backed by the ESP32 Preferences library.
- Created tests/mocks/Preferences.h to simulate persistent flash preferences on native hosts.
- Added tests/test_settings/test_settings.cpp unit tests to verify proper initialization, defaults, range constraints, and persistence.

Files:
- include/settings_manager.h
- src/settings_manager.cpp
- tests/mocks/Preferences.h
- tests/test_settings/test_settings.cpp

Why: Establishes the persistent settings configuration manager to support user settings across boot cycles.
